    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Ready to roll without breaking the bank! This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it starts up reliably, handles your daily commute with ease, and gets you from point A to point B without drama. Sure, it's not showroom-fresh, but it's honest, dependable transportation that won't let you down when it matters most. If you're looking for practical, affordable wheels with solid everyday reliability, this one deserves a serious look!",
