    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This is a genuinely exceptional vehicle offered in mint condition \u2014 one of the finest examples you're likely to find on the market. The exterior paintwork is flawless, retaining its original luster with no visible scratches, chips, or swirl marks. The interior is equally pristine: all upholstery, trim pieces, and surfaces are in like-new condition with no wear, staining, or fading. Mechanically, the car runs and drives perfectly \u2014 all systems are fully functional, with no warning lights, no unusual noises, and no deferred maintenance. Service records are available and up to date. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and cared for throughout its life, and it shows in every detail. If you're looking for a top-tier example that needs absolutely nothing, this is it.",
      "price": 48000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable, well-cared-for vehicle that delivers day in and day out? This good-condition gem is ready to be your next reliable ride! It runs smoothly, handles beautifully, and has been consistently maintained \u2014 you'll notice the attention to care the moment you get behind the wheel. There are a few minor cosmetic blemishes from normal use, but nothing that takes away from its overall appeal. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in fair condition, and we want to give you a complete and honest picture before you decide to purchase. The exterior shows its age \u2014 you'll notice several scratches and minor dents scattered across the body panels, and the paint has faded in certain areas, though the overall structure remains intact. The interior is functional but well-used, with visible wear on the seats, some scuffs on the dashboard trim, and a few small stains on the upholstery. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but you should expect that some components are showing their age and may require attention in the near future \u2014 we recommend a pre-purchase inspection so you know exactly what you're getting into. This is a practical, usable vehicle best suited for a buyer who understands they're getting a car that needs some TLC rather than a turnkey experience.",
      "price": 15500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "We're listing this vehicle honestly as a car in poor condition, and we want any potential buyer to have a completely accurate picture before reaching out. The exterior shows significant wear \u2014 there are multiple dents, scratches, and areas of rust that are visible on the body panels. The paint is faded and peeling in several spots, and the trim pieces show considerable deterioration. Mechanically, the vehicle has known issues that will require attention; it runs but is not in reliable daily-driver shape without repairs. The interior is worn with tears in the upholstery, cracked dashboard components, and some non-functional features. This listing is priced to reflect the car's true state \u2014 it's best suited for a buyer who is mechanically inclined, looking for a project vehicle, or needs basic transportation and is prepared to invest in repairs. Please reach out with any questions; we'd rather answer them upfront than have surprises at pickup.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Looking for a solid, no-frills daily driver that won't break the bank? This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it starts up reliably and gets you where you need to go, making it a practical choice for everyday use! You'll notice some cosmetic wear inside and out, as expected for its age and mileage, and there may be minor items that could use attention down the road. But if you're after dependable transportation at an honest price, this one deserves a look. Come take it for a spin!",
